<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="container hero-content">
    <span class="hero-eyebrow">REGÊ ENGENHARIA</span>
    <h1>PROJETANDO ESPAÇOS,<br />CONSTRUINDO SONHOS</h1>
    <p>Da concepção à chave na mão, cuidamos de todo o processo para você focar no que realmente importa.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="https://wa.me/5547992184100?text=Olá!%20Gostaria%20de%20conversar%20sobre%20um%20projeto." class="btn hero-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Falar com Especialista</a>
      <a href="#portfolio" class="btn btn-secondary hero-btn-sec">Ver Projetos</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 85vh;
    min-height: 600px;
    background-image: url('/images/hero-rege.png');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(27, 36, 48, 0.92) 20%, rgba(27, 36, 48, 0.5) 100%);
  }
  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    color: var(--white);
    max-width: 850px;
    margin-left: 0;
    text-align: left;
    padding-top: 2rem;
  }
  .hero-eyebrow {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-hero);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: var(--sand);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease forwards;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-hero);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--white);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    animation: fadeInUp 1s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1) forwards;
  }
  .hero p {
    font-family: var(--font-accent);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: var(--sand);
    line-height: 1.5;
    animation: fadeInUp 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1) forwards;
  }
  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    animation: fadeInUp 1.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1) forwards;
  }
  .hero-btn {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
  }
  .hero-btn-sec {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    color: var(--white);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
  }
  .hero-btn-sec:hover {
    background-color: var(--white);
    color: var(--navy);
    border-color: var(--white);
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      height: auto;
      padding: 6rem 0;
    }
    .hero-content {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .hero-actions {
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
